configuration.query_insert:
SELECT A.*,
                                          B.rec_add_ts as ZIW_REC_ADD_TS
                                   FROM   dwt_edw.cat_two_demo A
                                          JOIN dwt_edw.t_rec_hist B
                                            ON A.rec_hist_gid = B.rec_hist_gid
                                   WHERE  prcs_gid IN ( 998877 )
                                          AND rec_add_ts > Cast(
                                              cdc_start_time AS
                                              TIMESTAMP) and rec_add_ts <=Cast(
                                              cdc_end_time AS
                                              TIMESTAMP)
configuration.query_update:
SELECT A.*,B.REC_ADD_TS AS ZIW_REC_ADD_TS
        FROM   dwt_edw.cat_two_demo A
               INNER JOIN (SELECT TEMP.fname              AS TFNAME,
                                  TEMP.lname              AS TLNAME,
                                  ( TEMP.rec_eff_dt - 1 ) AS TREC_EXPRN_DT,
                                  TEMP.rec_add_ts         AS REC_ADD_TS
                           FROM   (SELECT C.*,
                                          D.rec_add_ts
                                   FROM   dwt_edw.cat_two_demo C
                                          JOIN dwt_edw.t_rec_hist D
                                            ON C.rec_hist_gid = D.rec_hist_gid
                                   WHERE  prcs_gid IN ( 998877 )
                                          AND rec_add_ts > Cast(
                                              cdc_start_time AS
                                              TIMESTAMP) and rec_add_ts <=Cast(
                                              cdc_end_time AS
                                              TIMESTAMP)
                                  ) TEMP) B
                           ON A.fname = B.tfname
                          AND A.lname = B.tlname
                          AND A.rec_exprn_dt = B.trec_exprn_dt
